Network Traffic in Cybersecurity
Suspicious Traffic Indicators

High packet rate

Unusual ports

Unknown IP addresses

Repeated failed connections

Large outbound transfers

Common Network Traffic Attacks
Attack	Traffic Behavior
DDoS	Traffic flood
Port Scan	Sequential port hits
MITM	Intercepted packets
Data Exfiltration	Large outbound flow
Malware C2	Periodic beaconing
Normal vs Malicious Traffic
Normal Traffic	Malicious Traffic
Predictable	Irregular
Known ports	Random ports
Known IPs	Unknown IPs
Steady flow	Spikes
